reviewText: Def Jam waz one of the funniest showz of all times. I like all the shows , especially Def Jams earlier shows watching comedians such as Bernie Mac, Joe Torrey, Dave Chappelle, and Chris Tucker etc.
Title: Def Comedy Jam: All 11 Episodes

reviewText: Surprisingly these CDs hold up very well, even 7 years later.  Mind you, there are parts in there that you have to think about, being that CD was made 7 years ago, but the comedy is timeless for Aries Spears, Mike Epps, Bill Bellamy, Leslie, et. al.Thank you folks for making us laugh
Title: Def Comedy Jam: All 11 Episodes

reviewText: I was actually shocked that it was good! The only let down is that Mike Epps, who is not that funny individually, was the host. He is no Martin or DL man he is not even a Joe Torre. All in all the new comdians and some old were funny!
